OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain will continue across western and
OL,7,Fsome northern parts of Scotland, but
OL,8,Fclearing northwards. Otherwise, it is
OL,9,Fdry elsewhere with clear spells. A few
OL,10,Ffog patches forming across southern
OL,11,FEngland. Not as chilly as previous
OL,12,Fnights.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FPlenty of very warm
OL,15,Fsunshine once again across much of
OL,16,FEngland and Wales, with temperatures
OL,17,Fwell above average. Mostly dry for
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland and Scotland though
OL,19,Fgenerally cloudier here.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
